			<p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-300 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
				Security that ships with your code
			</p>
			<p class="text-lg text-slate-400 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
				Our AI security agents scan every commit, every dependency, every container — catching vulnerabilities before they reach production. With human oversight from seasoned DevSecOps engineers.
			</p>
			<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
				<Button variant="primary" size="lg" href="/contact">Book Security Assessment</Button>
				<Button variant="outline" size="lg" href="#services">Explore Services</Button>
